===Etymology===
Cognate with {{och-l|驚|to be afraid; to scare}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}); the sense "to be on guard" is the endoactive of {{och-l|驚}}. See there for more.

{{och-l|儆|to warn; to guard against}} is the same word.

